::
::  +print-sections: renders a list of sections as tang
::
::    prints the longform documentation
++  print-sections
  |=  sections=(list sect)
  ^-  tang
  =|  out=tang
  |-
  ?~  sections  out
  =.  out
    ;:  weld
      out
      `tang`[%leaf ""]~
      (print-section i.sections)
    ==
  $(sections t.sections)
::
::  +print-section: renders a sect as a tang
++  print-section
  |=  section=sect
  ^-  tang
  %+  turn  section
  |=  =pica
  ^-  tank
  ?:  p.pica
    [%leaf (trip q.pica)]
  [%leaf "    {(trip q.pica)}"]
